title: Counter-Strike 1.6 No-Steam v48 standalone client
description:
Counter-Strike 1.6 No-Steam v48 standalone client

-has updated cracked files so nosteam can play with steam players on the same server again

-also includes HLDS v48 cracks so you can run your own server on the new protocol

-around 700mb~ once extracted

-v35 digitalzone release cracked to accept the new v48 protocol and is tested working Nov 2008

-no password

-extract folder, double click and play!

This will only work on new cracked nosteam servers, for old v47 protocol servers, get one of the older releases.
